Napoli lost 1-0 at home to Lazio in the Coppa Italia semi-final on Wednesday .
Napoli president Aurelio De Laurentiis has threatened to send his players to a training camp 'for an unlimited period of time' if they don't improve between now and the end of the season .
The defeat also increased pressure on coach Rafael Benitez, who led Napoli to third place in Serie A last season .